![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/86e79eee-410a-4fbf-9b0a-3a4c69864158/Screenshot+2025-08-15+092321.jpg)

[Deadline](https://deadline.com/2025/08/scary-movie-anna-faris-regina-hall-1236489539/) reports core _Scary Movie_ actresses Regina Hall and Anna Faris are confirmed to return as their iconic characters, Brenda Meeks and Cindy Campbell, for a new installment of the comedy franchise driven by the Wayans Brothers. The project marks a major reunion for Keenen, Shawn, and Marlon Wayans, who are collaborating on a new original script, with Keenen Ivory Wayans also set to produce. Michael Tiddes, a long-time Wayans collaborator who directed films like _A Haunted House_, will direct the new movie.

